{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "19", "m": "05", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "10", "M": "51", "S": "36"}}, "news": [{"title": "Green nod delay holds up Thiruvanthapuram airport expansion", "para": "Expansion of Thiruvananthapuram International Airport's Terminal 2 is delayed. Environmental clearance is pending with state authorities. The process involves multiple scrutiny stages. This delay impacts the planned April 2025 construction start. The airport operator needs this expansion for future passenger growth. Redevelopment includes terminal modernization, parking, and new facilities.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/thiruvananthapuram-airport-expansion-delayed-by-environmental-clearance-issues/131194811?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-1404617/131194811.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Rajkot civic body collects \u20b9152 crore advance taxes in 40 days", "para": "Rajkot Municipal Corporation has collected Rs 153 crore in advance property and water taxes for the 2026-27 financial year within 40 days. Digital payments led the collection, with significant discounts offered to early payers. This advance collection shows a steady increase from the previous year across all city zones.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/rajkot-municipal-corporation-collects-153-crore-in-advance-taxes-in-just-40-days/131193951?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-108366/131193951.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}, {"title": "Orissa high court stays suspension on sand quarry lessee", "para": "The Orissa High Court has ruled that statutory authorities cannot usurp powers not expressly conferred by law. The court stayed an interim suspension order on a sand quarry lessee, finding no provision in the Odisha Minor Mineral Concession Rules, 2016, for such immediate action pending adjudication of alleged violations.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/allied-industries/orissa-high-court-blocks-sand-quarry-lessees-suspension/131193831?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-1462183/131193831.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "allied-industries"}]}